    "summary": "RENTON, Wash., April 16, 2026--Today, Wizards of the Coast, a division of Hasbro (NASDAQ: HAS), announces Dungeon Masters, an all-new official Dungeons & Dragons actual play series debuting April 22 on YouTube with a two-episode premiere special. With weekly episodes that showcase official, unreleased D&D content, and innovative visuals that help viewers follow the action, Dungeon Masters is made to appeal to a wide audience of D&D veterans, newcomers and everyone in between.",
